{"tid":1814010,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候叫身邊既人今個新年唔好返大陸探親拜年","createTime":"2020-01-06T16:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T16:55:13.000Z","uid":252587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"219d9d310b1a41df27dbdea7a512b10f69e1a8b5","tid":1814010,"uid":252587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:26:46.000Z","msg":"香港懷疑感染個案增至21宗，<br />\n武漢仍只得59宗（真實數字一定唔止）。<br />\n<br />\n每年農曆新年都有大量香港人返中國探親拜年，<br />\n到時唔係中國人害死香港人，<br />\n而係香港人害死自己人，明知山有虎偏向虎山行。<br />\n<br />\n以我得知，身邊有淺黃朋友，佢地屋企人叫佢地一定要返去，雖然佢地唔想返，但基於孝順同習慣，佢地真係有動搖！<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日睇新聞都見到中國人係幾咁自私，有病拒入院，仲要周圍走，將病菌四圍傳播。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外附上黃藍口罩選擇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79hMsJz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79hMsJz.jpg&h=4399c92f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8420783c8683689d7f56948bb37e5413d92decf6","tid":1814010,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"1個月唔好接觸番過大陸既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6d959d34d2f7d6df2710bdba90601fb60c01e9","tid":1814010,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:28:31.000Z","msg":"返你老母 用個去字"},{"pid":"32cc16defbaa113c7bbe253f438a18a977d2ff5b","tid":1814010,"uid":252587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8420783c8683689d7f56948bb37e5413d92decf6","tid":1814010,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"1個月唔好接觸番過大陸既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:28:41.000Z","msg":"真係好難講...年年都有唔少同事新年會返